value: Breeds in the Galapagos Archipelago on Culpepper (Darwin), Wenman (Wolf), Santa Cruz (Indefatigable), South Plaza, San Cristobal (Chatham), and Espahola (Hood) Islands, and proba- bly on many of the other islands and their outlying rocks. Disperses far north across the Equator to the coast of Mexico.
refer: Peter's Checklist of the Birds of the World
